FBIS3-41264 "jptdd007__l94054" JPRS-TDD-94-007-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 14 February 1994 AFRICA BENIN Diplomat Questioned Following Discovery of Heroin at New York Airport AB1402114294 Paris AFP in English 0947 GMT 14 Feb 94 AB1402114294 Paris AFP Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Cotonou, 14 Feb (AFP) -- A Benin diplomat serving in the United States was questioned at New York Airport after being found with four kilos (eight pounds) of heroin, the Foreign Ministry said here Monday. The drug was hidden in the false bottom of a suitcase carried by Abdoul Karim as he arrived in the United States on February 3, the ministry added.
